# Testing conventions

- Vitest + React Testing Library for unit/integration; Playwright for e2e (e2e/ folder only).
- Query by role/label/text the way a user would — avoid data-testid unless there's no
  accessible alternative.
- Mock GraphQL with MockedProvider (one mock per test case). Mock REST with MSW handlers under
  __tests__/mocks.
- Test behavior, not implementation: assert on rendered output and user-visible state changes,
  not on internal hook calls.
- A new hook or non-trivial component is not done until it has a test — see docs/TESTING.md
  for exactly what needs coverage.
